definitions.definition: A somewhat liquid mess , often of food; a soft or semisolid substance.
( radio ) A mixture of noise produced by the harmonics of continuous-wave stations .
( surfing ) The foam of a breaker .
( geology ) A magmatic body containing a significant proportion of crystals suspended in the liquid phase or melt .

examples: Do you want me to back out the mush , bruv ?

main_definition: A somewhat liquid mess , often of food; a soft or semisolid substance.
secondary_definitions: ( radio ) A mixture of noise produced by the harmonics of continuous-wave stations .
( surfing ) The foam of a breaker .
( geology ) A magmatic body containing a significant proportion of crystals suspended in the liquid phase or melt .

definitions.definition: A food comprising cracked or rolled grains cooked in water or milk; porridge .
( rustic US ) Cornmeal cooked in water and served as a porridge or as a thick sidedish like grits or mashed potatoes.

main_definition: A food comprising cracked or rolled grains cooked in water or milk; porridge .

definitions.definition: A walk , especially across the snow with dogs .

main_definition: A walk , especially across the snow with dogs .

definitions.definition: ( British , slang , chiefly Southern England ) ( US , slang , chiefly Nonantum ) A form of address, normally to a man.
examples: Oy mush , come over here and gimme a hand with the motor.

definitions.definition: ( British , slang , chiefly Northern England , Australia ) The face .

definitions.definition: A cab driver who is the owner of their cab , and sometimes a small number of other cabs as well; a musher .
